title: Weekly Bedford Heights, Garfield Heights, Highland Hills, Bedford, Nor
posting_body: ['Happy Fathers Day.', 'Bedford Heights City Council had a meeting via zoom on Sunday, 06/19/22 at 6:00 PM.', 'Bedford Heights City Council had a meeting on Tuesday, 06/21/22 at 6:00 PM.', 'Warrensville Heights City Council had a meeting on the same day from 6:00 PM to 8:00 PM.', 'Bedford Heights City Council had a meeting via zoom on the same day, at 7:00 PM.', 'City of Bedford Seniors Club "Grab and Go or Stay" event occurred on Wednesday, 06/22/22 at 11:30 PM.', 'Bedford Summer Concert Series event occurred on the same day from 7:00 PM to 9:00 PM.', 'There was a high level of activity on the Bedford Heights, Garfield Heights, Highland Hills, Warrensville Heights and Maple Heights real estate market this week.', '20 single family homes and 2 condominiums were listed for sale.', '15 single family home listings were returned to market.', '16 single family home listing and 3 condominium listings changed to contract.', ' The price was reduced to 5 single family homes.', '20 single family home listings and 3 condominium listings began awaiting sale.', '1 single family home listing started awaiting rental.', '21 single family homes were sold.', '3 single family homes were rented.', '2 single family home listings were withdrawn.', '2 single family home listing were placed temporary off market.', '1 single family home listing expired.']
